{"lastModified":1752598114098,"uri":"c::28924311089::vessel::4fed3bb0-fb44-11ef-9630-fb128ba9f0fe","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia, Montenegro \n\nSeeking a perfect day on the sea? Then we should introduce you to M/Y CONTESSA  yacht. Princess Yachts is a leading British luxury yacht manufacturer with meticulous attention to detail, delivering unforgettable experiences. \n\nThe yacht has all of the equipment that you need for a perfect time on the sea, such as teak decks, teak on the flybridge, hydraulic swim bath platform that can carry a jet ski*. Flybridge is equipped with a refrigerator, sink, and electric barbecue. Furthermore, cabins are spacious and each one has their suite. The saloon, galley, and cabin are airconditioned. The yacht is powered by two Cummins engines with a total of 1100 hp.\n\nOn a day trip you will be provided with safety instructions upon arriving on board, drinks such as beer, Coca-Cola, soft drinks, and wine** You will additionally get snacks and seasonal fruits. Snorkelling equipment, paddleboard, life jackets, TV, and stereo are standard equipment of the yacht. If you feel the need for anything extra you may arrange it specifically with your agent.","blueprint":{"name":"CONTESSA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fed3bb0-fb44-11ef-9630-fb128ba9f0fe::assets::a0b26e40-fb48-11ef-a77c-5778349b56fa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fed3bb0-fb44-11ef-9630-fb128ba9f0fe::assets::a0bbe420-fb48-11ef-8f34-09731670097e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fed3bb0-fb44-11ef-9630-fb128ba9f0fe::assets::a0bb20d0-fb48-11ef-8f34-09731670097e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fed3bb0-fb44-11ef-9630-fb128ba9f0fe::assets::a0bb6ef0-fb48-11ef-983e-ad7243aeca07/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fed3bb0-fb44-11ef-9630-fb128ba9f0fe::assets::a0baaba0-fb48-11ef-8f34-09731670097e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fed3bb0-fb44-11ef-9630-fb128ba9f0fe::a